txt.en: Returned to Kishâtu with the various plants
Kishâtu has asked you to gather various plants nearby in Urash Dâr.
Return to Kishâtu with the plants you have collected for her.
Return to Kishâtu with the plants

'Ah, you have returned, and it appears with the plants that I requested.'

You hand the plants to Kishâtu.

'Thank you, [placeholder]. These will be put to good use'
Returned to Kishâtu with the plants
Kishâtu has asked for your help gathering various plants she needs from the area.

'Greetings [placeholder].

'If you are willing, I could use your help as we are running low on some of our supplies here.

'I am in need of some red and yellow wild-flowers, as well as some berries. You can find the wild-flowers nearby, but you may find berries along the river's edge.'
